OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Girls excluded
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas Afghan secondary schools
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freopen                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban have excluded girls from   
OL,6, Afghan secondary schools, with only    
OL,7, boys and male teachers allowed back    
OL,8, into classrooms.                       
OL,10,FSchoolgirls told the BBC they were     
OL,11,Fdevastated not to be returning.        
OL,12,F"Everything looks very dark," one said.
OL,14,FTaliban officials who seized power last
OL,15,Fmonth said they were working to reach a
OL,16,Fdecision on the matter.                
OL,18,FMany fear a return of the regime of the
OL,19,F1990s when the Taliban severely        
OL,20,Frestricted girls' and women's rights.  
